data.description: Welcome to this meticulously maintained 3 bed, 2.5 bath zero lot home on the east side of Iowa City! Designed by Neumann Monson. Large picture windows and high ceilings give a feeling of peace and spaciousness throughout the open kitchen, dining room, and living room. Easy access to the walk-out patio and small yard. The kitchen is equipped with a large island/breakfast bar, granite countertops, and loads of cabinet space. Primary suite on the main has a lovely ensuite with large walk-in tile shower, dual vanities, and a spacious walk-in closet. A dedicated laundry room with built-in cabinets is located on the main level for easy aging in place. You will enjoy so much shelving and storage. The finished lower-level has two bedrooms, a full bath, and a large family room with daylight windows for a comfortable retreat. Oversized two-car garage rounds out the package here in the heart of Churchill Meadows. Easy access to West Branch, Iowa City, grocery, and more.
